.TH "zynqmp_disp_blend_layer_set_csc" 9 "zynqmp_disp_blend_layer_set_csc" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
zynqmp_disp_blend_layer_set_csc \- Configure colorspace conversion for layer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" zynqmp_disp_blend_layer_set_csc
.BI "(struct zynqmp_disp_blend *blend "  ","
.BI "struct zynqmp_disp_layer *layer "  ","
.BI "const u16 *coeffs "  ","
.BI "const u32 *offsets "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "blend" 12
Blender object
.IP "layer" 12
The layer
.IP "coeffs" 12
Colorspace conversion matrix
.IP "offsets" 12
Colorspace conversion offsets
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Configure the input colorspace conversion matrix and offsets for the \fIlayer\fP.
Columns of the matrix are automatically swapped based on the input format to
handle RGB and YCrCb components permutations.
